ActCanadian Air Transport Security Authority Act
PrecisAppointment of RON PATMORE of South Monaghan, Ontario, to be a director of the board of directors of the Canadian Air Transport Security Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Darrel G. Smith.
